Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爷回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爷回府
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公今日为何如此高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}温酒上菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爷 我要痛饮一番哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 酒菜已经摆上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回主公 半个时辰以前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来了个远道的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦 自称是主公的老友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吩咐在下温酒上菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}姓甚名谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人不肯道出姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下不知虚实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不敢得罪他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在 此人大概已经半醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阁下何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董相国祸乱长安城
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王司徒暗设连环计
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陈公台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此计好不恶毒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}司徒大人就不怕引发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}灭族大祸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你刚才吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}兄台欲救天下 功垂万古
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.72,0:01:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下深表敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪里哪里 贤弟请
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乱世遇故人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是喜从天降啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我听人说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你投奔曹孟德共襄大义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么跑到长安来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那曹阿瞒表面上忠义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其实是个奸险之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已经弃他而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说来话长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}离开曹操之后 我是浪迹四方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寻找能让我辅佐的贤明主公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是数月下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}除了帐下奸雄与路边骸骨之外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是一无所获呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无奈之中 我又来到了长安城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是刚到长安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就在酒馆里听人议论
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说什么董卓和吕布在争一个美女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}名字叫什么貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这貂蝉不是阁下的义女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}顿时啊 我什么都明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我什么都瞒不住贤弟你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一眼就看破了乾坤哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}兄台 事情进展如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大局已定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只等他们二人反目成仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}互相拼杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下一步 兄台想怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正想向贤弟请教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下想 要除掉董贼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}关键还在吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}外面何人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我家主公还没回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 义父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫已经备好了美酒佳肴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就等你入席了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不必多言 请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父大人 小人大祸临头了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}未必
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不知道 凤仪亭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓他是不会宽恕我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请义父出个主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是万万没有想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这世间第一英雄吕奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟也如此不堪哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布啊吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}莫非你自己都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自己有多大的本事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}依我看 你根本不用害怕董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相反那董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更应该害怕你才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是我的老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陈宫 字公台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他上知天文 下晓地理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}饱览古今 胸怀韬略
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先若得公台相助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必能成就一番大业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请公台先生教我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军 世人皆知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人中吕布 马中赤兔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}加上你一杆方天画戟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军足可以无敌于天下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是不知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军有无胆略而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那董卓淫我之女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夺将军之妻 行禽兽之事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}令天下人切齿之恨哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫如今老矣 不足为道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是将军你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是英雄豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂能受此奇耻大辱哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓他欺君篡位 祸乱朝纲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}堪称是我们大汉四百年来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从未有过的巨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果将军你能够将他除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不但可以为你自己正名雪耻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更可为我们大汉创建四百年来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从未有过的功勋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫夜观天象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只见紫薇星弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有一贼星陨落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正应了董卓气数已尽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他活不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不瞒二位 凭我手中方天画戟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要诛杀董卓如屠猪狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只担心 他是我义父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我怕世人会说我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}弑父弑君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓他姓董 吕将军姓吕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这何谓父子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他董卓执戟追杀你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪里有一丝一毫的父子之情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小女貂蝉身陷魔窟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}日夜思念着将军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军如若能除此巨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不但为大汉建功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且可以和貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终生幸福哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这于公于私
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都是功德无量的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二位直言吧 我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉天子诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诛杀董贼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国 相国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大喜事 大喜事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀相国 臣刚刚奉召进宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在后宫见过太后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太后亲口对臣说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天子孱弱 龙体多病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}实在不堪坐朝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}时下朝野纷乱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唯有相国才能治理天下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太后决定让天子禅位给相国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恭请相国加尊九五
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}改朝称帝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太后真的肯让天子退位了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过她唯一的条件就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请相国善待她们孤儿寡母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保证她和天子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一辈子衣食无虞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那好说呀 那太好说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要是她肯让天子退位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赏她一个终生富贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣恭喜相国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦不 臣恭喜陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}光是有这个太后的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恐怕不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那些百官们什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有王允那些个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前朝的公卿大臣们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们会不会启奏太后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阻拦天子退位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太后亲口对臣说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由她出面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}令王允亲自起草退位诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀相国
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允领着一干老臣 前来觐见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有请
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国有令 请众臣觐见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣王允等 叩见陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叩见陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家就是一个相国
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们为何要以陛下相称哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣等奉太后懿旨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}草拟了汉帝的退位诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恭请陛下以天下苍生为念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}改元换代 即位九五
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好好好 王允啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你都替咱家把这国名和年号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都已经拟好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天意所至 万众归心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣等顺应天意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愿为陛下效犬马之劳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣等顺应天意 恭请陛下即位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好好 王允啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在这就多谢了 多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将来我坐上了皇位以后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们几位都是开国功臣 都是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 平身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先哪 你也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将 前来向义父请罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将罪无可赦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请义父剥夺末将所有爵位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}罚往边关为卒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家早就跟你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家早晚要即大位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}罪将恭喜陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先啊 过去的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们一概不提了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}记着 只要你忠于咱家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家仍然视你为子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仍然是会让你位极人臣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仍然会让你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有享不完的荣华富贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿臣拜谢父皇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看到了吧 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这可是太后给咱家下的诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}后日午时 咱家可要做皇上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你哪 我的心肝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可就要做蝉贵妃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看看 看看可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到咱家的卧榻上来看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快点来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家等 不 是朕等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿臣在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿臣在想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父当上皇帝之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿臣怎么帮义父剿灭各地乱贼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对 这个事你是得好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家即位以后嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}肯定有很多诸侯不服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}肯定他们要 要起兵闹事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个时候可是你建业的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿臣明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日祭天大礼 着你左右护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不得远离
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿臣遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陛下起驾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣等恭迎圣驾 臣等恭迎圣驾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恭迎圣驾 恭迎圣驾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好好 好好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爱卿们好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爱卿们好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这我怎么没见到王司徒 王大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听旨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}国贼董卓 亵渎朝纲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}祸乱天下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诏忠勇之士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诛杀逆贼董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀 杀国贼 杀国贼 杀国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先何在 奉先何在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉旨杀贼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先何在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天子恩旨 只杀董卓一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}余者不论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们快快放下兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}归顺圣上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}苍天啊 先帝啊 大汉有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}万岁 万岁 万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:21:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣等叩见陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吾皇万岁万岁万万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}平身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣王允谨奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}国贼董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经在正阳宫门外伏诛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我大汉玉宇澄清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天下万民欢庆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宣旨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}皇帝有旨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}册封王允为朝廷太师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}领相国 摄国治政
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}册封吕布为忠义侯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}授奋威将军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}钦此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣 领旨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣领旨 叩谢天恩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我被那董老贼玷污过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.87,0:23:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军不会嫌弃我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 龌龊的是我吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而你才是天下最圣洁的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我岂不还在认贼作父吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.18,0:23:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不但是我最爱的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更是我的救星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.39,0:23:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我生命的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.68,0:24:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太师 董卓部将
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.38,0:24:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李傕 郭汜二人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已成惊弓之鸟 溃退于边地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.49,0:24:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们畏惧太师之威 吕布之勇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.59,0:24:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不敢与朝廷相杭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.29,0:24:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}决定上表乞降
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不成 我谁都可以赦免
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.57,0:24:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唯独不赦李傕 郭汜二贼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.67,0:24:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.67,0:24:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}实在是太可恨了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.48,0:24:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀了我多少臣工
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.38,0:24:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓的恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.98,0:24:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大半是这两个人做下的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.09,0:24:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不赦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.29,0:25:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太师 还望以大局为念
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.19,0:25:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可拘于一时义愤
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.19,0:25:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓虽然已死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.59,0:25:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李郭二人尚有十万西凉骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.10,0:25:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}常言道 狗急跳墙 穷寇勿迫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.90,0:25:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还望太师恩准他们投降
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.57,0:25:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以免把他们逼上绝路
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.88,0:25:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我非但要将他们逼上绝路
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.38,0:25:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还要送他们上死路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.58,0:25:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公台啊 你想一想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.89,0:25:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}贼军不灭 皇威何在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.49,0:25:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}斩草除根 昭大义于天下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.50,0:25:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太师 李郭二人都是西凉上将
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.20,0:25:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}万万不可轻视啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.97,0:25:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有奋威将军吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.58,0:25:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李 郭二贼乃待死鼠辈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.38,0:25:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布听令
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.49,0:26:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将在
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.69,0:26:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我令你 带领本部人马
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.49,0:26:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三日之内出征边地
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.09,0:26:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}务必全歼西凉残部
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.00,0:26:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不得有误
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.30,0:26:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将领命
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.18,0:26:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.38,0:26:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.98,0:26:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允不许我们归降朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.79,0:26:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听说还要派大军来攻杀我们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}弟兄们 你们看怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.99,0:26:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董相一死
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.09,0:26:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉那边即刻倒向了朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.99,0:26:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且还断了我们的粮草后路
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.30,0:26:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们现在是战无可战
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.10,0:26:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}守无可守
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.10,0:26:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看 不如把银两分喽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.40,0:26:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让弟兄们回家避难去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.70,0:26:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二哥也不想想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.11,0:26:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是现在逃回乡里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.71,0:27:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个亭长就能把咱们给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.18,0:27:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家只有聚在一起 才会有生路
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.68,0:27:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这话说得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.88,0:27:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在我们手上握有十二万重兵
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.69,0:27:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝对不可以坐以待毙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.69,0:27:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不如我们拼它个鱼死网破
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.39,0:27:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}日夜兼程 攻下长安
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.19,0:27:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.70,0:27:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}攻上去 剿灭奸贼 杀
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.18,0:28:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把城门撞开
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.61,0:28:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.71,0:28:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李傕 郭汜率领西凉军已经破城
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.81,0:28:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}城内守军纷纷投降
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.88,0:28:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们大势已去了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.89,0:28:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}悔不听贤弟建言
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.79,0:28:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一招不慎 满盘皆输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.66,0:28:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}兄台此时再说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.70,0:29:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有什么用处
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.40,0:29:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我估计 不出半个时辰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.60,0:29:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们就会拿下皇宫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.50,0:29:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}擒拿天子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.71,0:29:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这 这万万不成
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.31,0:29:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要亲自领军去皇宫护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.81,0:29:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你去郿坞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.41,0:29:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}速召吕布前来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.58,0:29:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 太师啊 贼军势力太大
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.49,0:29:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此时召吕布回来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.09,0:29:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只怕是来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.99,0:29:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不如
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.09,0:29:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}兄台
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.99,0:29:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不如你赶紧携天子与太后
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.29,0:29:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出城避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.40,0:29:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 西凉军骁勇善战
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.70,0:29:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天子一旦弃城而出
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.30,0:29:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荒郊野外无处可守
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.91,0:29:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早晚便落入贼军手中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.71,0:29:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}莫不如守城待援为是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.22,0:29:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你速去召吕布前来增援
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.08,0:29:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 这
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.29,0:29:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.19,0:30:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手 住手 住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.20,0:30:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手 停
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.31,0:30:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天子何在
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.71,0:30:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们要面见天子陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.21,0:30:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天子在此 尔等不得放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.92,0:30:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}启禀天子陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.62,0:30:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等并不是要谋反
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.29,0:30:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只是陛下身边出了个奸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.59,0:30:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们要诛杀奸贼 匡扶汉业
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.79,0:30:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁是奸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.70,0:30:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是你身边的王允
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.00,0:30:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人谋害董相
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.70,0:30:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}屠戮忠良 独擅朝政 祸国殃民
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.31,0:30:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫反倒成了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.31,0:30:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}屠戮忠良 祸国殃民的奸贼了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.92,0:31:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陛下 只要你交出王允
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.39,0:31:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等决不会伤害于你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.60,0:31:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫若是下城受戮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.90,0:31:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们会善待天子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.70,0:31:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要你打开城门
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.61,0:31:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等就不会为难于天子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.79,0:31:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}苍天啊 先帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.70,0:31:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣王允以死报国了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.81,0:32:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奸贼 老夫来也
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.22,0:32:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快 给我把王允碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.60,0:32:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.96,0:32:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先 奉先哪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.80,0:32:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陈宫 出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.40,0:32:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看见京城大火冲天
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.71,0:32:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}完了 全都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.51,0:32:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}京城陷落 天子被擒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.91,0:32:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王允也已经以身殉国了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.22,0:32:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我立刻去城外大营
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.72,0:32:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}领兵回攻长安 援救天子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.12,0:32:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 等一下 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.42,0:32:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这里现在还有多少兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.72,0:32:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}步军两万 骑兵八千
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.49,0:32:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不够哇 贼军势大
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.00,0:32:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且他们现在已经关闭城门
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.00,0:32:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居高坚守 根本攻不进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.30,0:33:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.62,0:33:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.71,0:33:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军啊 今日之祸
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.31,0:33:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只怪那王允他不听我言哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.42,0:33:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他拒绝李 郭二人的归降
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.12,0:33:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才导致今天贼军破城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.72,0:33:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先生有何见教
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.19,0:33:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.00,0:33:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你肯听我的计策
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.40,0:33:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我愿辅助将军
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.90,0:33:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}共创一番功名大业
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.90,0:33:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请先生示下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.31,0:33:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.91,0:33:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}依我看这次京城陷落之后
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.11,0:33:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天下必定会再度大乱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.81,0:33:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}群雄并起 刀兵横行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.42,0:33:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只怕是几十年天下也不得太平
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.12,0:33:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕将军 你英勇过人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.62,0:33:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拥有数万兵甲
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.53,0:33:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们不如暂离长安
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.13,0:34:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}南下荆襄 占据一城池
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.10,0:34:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作为立足根据
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.00,0:34:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后 我们再
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.70,0:34:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}招兵买马 扩大实力
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.60,0:34:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}逐鹿中原 建功立业
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.01,0:34:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布愿意听先生盼咐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.01,0:34:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.72,0:34:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尽快起行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.72,0:34:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先生稍候
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.52,0:34:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}容我稍做收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.92,0:34:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 时间如此紧迫
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.33,0:34:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道你还贪恋那些金银细软不成
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.33,0:34:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 在下宁可不要金银
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.60,0:34:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但必须携上夫人同行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.90,0:34:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.60,0:34:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.21,0:34:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.23,0:35:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.23,0:35:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.04,0:35:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹老太爷进城了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.20,0:35:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪个曹老太爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.91,0:35:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操的父亲曹嵩 借道徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.31,0:35:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前往兖州与曹操团圆 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.52,0:35:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们赶紧布置仪仗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.62,0:35:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安排酒宴
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.92,0:35:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以王公之礼迎接曹嵩
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.73,0:35:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 我必须亲自出城相迎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.13,0:35:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲 您重病在身 就别出城相迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.83,0:35:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿我代您出迎就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.43,0:35:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来的是曹操的父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.60,0:35:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我岂能不亲自相迎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.51,0:35:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们与曹操素无来往
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.91,0:35:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您以礼相待就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.61,0:35:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何必要持以王公之礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.51,0:35:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你以为我愿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.02,0:36:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是不得不如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.92,0:36:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.62,0:36:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}徐州乃四战之地呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.42,0:36:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}北面的袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.13,0:36:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}东面的袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.99,0:36:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再加上曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.43,0:36:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们都贪图我们徐州啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.83,0:36:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而我们兵寡将弱
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.00,0:36:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪个诸侯都得罪不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.21,0:36:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲既然知道他贪图徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.41,0:36:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何还对他献殷勤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.71,0:36:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各方诸侯中
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.72,0:36:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操的兵将最为精悍
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.12,0:36:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其州府离徐州也最近
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.52,0:36:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其称霸之野心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.12,0:36:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是最为如火如荼哇
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.13,0:36:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们灭又灭不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.53,0:36:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}打又打不过他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.84,0:36:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.30,0:36:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就得向他们示以恩宠
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.41,0:37:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}设法化敌为友
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.91,0:37:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.81,0:37:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才能守得住徐州的太平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.22,0:37:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.94,0:37:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军 将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.31,0:37:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各位弟兄 我等本是黄巾余党
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.21,0:37:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然投靠了陶谦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.61,0:37:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}却一直不受重用
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.41,0:37:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看哪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.32,0:37:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}日后除了替他战死沙场以外
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.42,0:37:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会有什么出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.72,0:37:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥说得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.72,0:37:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们一不做二不休
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.92,0:37:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀了曹嵩取了钱财
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.22,0:37:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们到五凤山落草去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.93,0:37:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}过神仙般的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.73,0:37:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么样 嗯 好好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.13,0:37:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.93,0:37:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走 走 走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.91,0:38:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.38,0:38:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你老人家死得好惨哪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.12,0:38:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孩儿对不住你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.33,0:38:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}苍天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.23,0:38:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹将军 主公出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.53,0:38:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何如此痛呼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.23,0:38:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚刚得报
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.13,0:38:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹老太爷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.13,0:38:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被贼人们给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.28,0:38:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被贼人给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.04,0:38:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨天还接到老太爷口信
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.74,0:38:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说徐州刺史陶谦派亲兵来护送
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.91,0:38:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天就可以到达兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.71,0:38:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与主公父子相会
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.41,0:38:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这怎么会被贼人给杀害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.42,0:38:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀害老太爷的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.22,0:38:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是给他护驾的张铠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.62,0:38:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个陶谦 真是昏昧到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.63,0:39:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}观人不明驭下无方
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.43,0:39:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟然铸此大错
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.23,0:39:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.24,0:39:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孩儿不孝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.34,0:39:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孩儿对不住你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.21,0:39:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荀彧啊 主公在里边
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.02,0:39:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}痛苦万分 捶胸顿足
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.42,0:39:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等怎么劝都劝不住
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.42,0:39:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你到里边宽慰他一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.92,0:39:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他可是最听你的话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.83,0:39:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不急不急
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.73,0:39:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}且让主公再痛哭一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.33,0:39:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.34,0:39:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲 父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.04,0:39:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹嵩 曹老太爷
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.51,0:39:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被张铠给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.11,0:39:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹老太爷眼看第二天就进入兖州地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.82,0:39:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁料张铠那贼将见财起意
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.82,0:40:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}趁夜伙同部下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.92,0:40:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀了老太爷十二口人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.93,0:40:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}劫走了全部金银财物
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.63,0:40:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到五凤山落草为寇去了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.73,0:40:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爷 老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.73,0:40:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲 你怎么了 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.34,0:40:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}完了 完了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.10,0:40:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如今全完了 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.04,0:40:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你别着急啊 别着急呀父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.05,0:40:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都怪我 都怪我瞎了眼哪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.02,0:40:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忘记了张铠是贼匪的余党啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.92,0:40:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我本想交结曹操这个袅雄
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.13,0:40:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁知弄巧成拙
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.23,0:40:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惹下了滔天巨祸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.70,0:41:12.09,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}天地之间莽苍苍
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.09,0:41:23.19,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}一时多少豪强
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.19,0:41:29.61,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}胜负由来不久长
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.61,0:41:39.02,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}去如大江水
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.02,0:41:50.94,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}奔流向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.64,0:42:16.52,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}书藏万卷胸次广
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.52,0:42:28.75,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}细数百代兴亡
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.75,0:42:34.62,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}功成身退早还乡
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.62,0:42:43.99,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}平淡心中事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.99,0:42:56.62,lrc,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}无语对斜阳
